De Beers Will Decide on $1.4 Billion Venetia Expansion Project in Mid-2012

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-07-20T08:51:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-20/de-beers-will-decide-on-1-4-billion-venetia-expansion-project-in-mid-2012.html
De Beers  will submit a 10 billion
rand expansion plan at its Venetia mine in South Africa to the
board “towards the middle of 2012 for final decision,” the
company’s South African Chairman Barend Petersen said in a
speech in Johannesburg today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  